latestPosts.caption:
She is not just my best friend — she is my soul sister. She was the first person from my side to visit me in the US, crossing miles just to be with me, to remind me that l’m never alone. She have always been my safe space — the first person I call when I’m not okay, the one who listens without judgment and loves without conditions. Thank you for making me feel like family, for showing up for me every single time. I’ll forever be grateful for you. Here’s to our beautiful friendship - today and always🥹♥️ Happy birthday deepa♥️ I love you @deepagowdaa ♥️
